app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online. Figure S1: Certification of S. hexaphylla leaves from National Institute of Biological Resources, Figure S2: Results of genetic analysis of the plant material S. hexaphylla, Figures S3–S7: 1D ( 1H, 13C-NMR) and 2D (COSY, HMQC and HMBC) spectra of compound 1, Figures S8–S12: 1D ( 1H, 13C-NMR) and 2D (COSY, HMQC and HMBC) spectra of compound 2, Figures S13 and S14: The HPLC-ELSD and HPLC-UV chromatogram of EtOH extract and standard compounds 1 and 2.
